          <h4 class="title">Return Policy</h4>
          <p>At Harisree Handlooms, we aim to provide you with high-quality handloom products and a smooth shopping experience. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, we're here to assist with a clear and hassle-free return process.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Return Eligibility</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Returns are accepted only for products that are damaged, defective, or incorrectly delivered.</li>
            <li>The item must be unused, unwashed, and in its original packaging with tags intact.</li>
            <li>Return requests must be initiated within <strong>7 days</strong> from the date of delivery.</li>
            <li>A valid proof of purchase (invoice or order ID) is required for all returns.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Non-returnable Items</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Products that have been used, washed, or altered in any way.</li>
            <li>Items purchased during sales, promotions, or discounts unless received in a damaged or defective condition.</li>
            <li>Customized or made-to-order handloom products.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Return Procedure</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:harisreehandlooms@gmail.com">harisreehandlooms@gmail.com</a> with your order ID, reason for return, and clear pictures of the product (if applicable).</li>
            <li>Our team will review your request and respond within 24â€“48 hours with further instructions.</li>
            <li>If your return is approved, you will be required to ship the product back to us at your own expense (unless the product is defective or wrongly delivered).</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Return Address</h4>
          <p>The return address will be provided in the return approval email. Please ensure proper packaging to avoid damage during transit.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Refund After Return</h4>
          <p>Once we receive and inspect the returned item, we will notify you regarding the status of your return. If approved, a refund or replacement will be initiated as per our <a href="/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a>.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Exchange Policy</h4>
          <p>Currently, we do not offer direct exchanges. If you wish to exchange an item, please return the original product and place a new order.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Contact Us</h4>
